🚀 Features
🌍 Multi-Mode Support: Includes 4 dedicated AI personas:

General Chat

Coder Assistant

Philosophy Bot

Helpdesk Agent

💾 Persistent Chat History: Chats are saved using localStorage, allowing users to revisit past conversations.

🌓 Light/Dark Mode Toggle: UI includes theme switching with preference remembered across sessions.

📁 File Upload & Camera Capture: Users can upload .txt, .pdf, .docx files or capture photos directly from the webcam.

💬 Real-Time Typing Animation: AI responses appear with a dynamic typing animation for better UX.

📱 Responsive Design: Fully functional across all screen sizes — mobile, tablet, and desktop.

🧠 Powered by Gemini AI: Utilizes Gemini API for powerful and context-aware responses.

🛠️ Technologies Used
Frontend: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (ES6)

AI Backend: Gemini API (via HTTP requests)

Hosting: Cloudflare Pages

Storage: localStorage for user preferences and chat history

Media Handling: HTML5 FileReader, Webcam Access via getUserMedia

